WEBVTT

00:08:29.721 --> 00:08:34.628
ready to be taken up again
in our own convulsive moment.

00:08:35.744 --> 00:08:38.260
That conversation is broken.

00:08:38.793 --> 00:08:42.681
The old questions
are harmful and divisive.

00:08:43.486 --> 00:08:46.003
So how do we get from that conversation

00:08:46.027 --> 00:08:50.576
to one that's more likely to get us
closer to a world that is fairer,

00:08:50.600 --> 00:08:52.171
that is more just,

00:08:52.195 --> 00:08:53.711
that's more secure?

00:08:55.036 --> 00:08:57.375
I want to suggest that what we have to do

00:08:57.399 --> 00:09:01.088
is one of the hardest things
that any society can do: